FFmpeg README
-------------

1) Documentation
----------------

* Read the documentation in the doc/ directory in git.
  You can also view it online at http://ffmpeg.org/documentation.html

2) Licensing
------------

* See the LICENSE file.

3) Build and Install
--------------------

* See the INSTALL file.

4) Install depts

apt-get install yasm deb-multimedia-keyring libfaac-dev  libgsm1-dev  libmp3lame-dev  libtheora-dev  libvorbis-dev  libx264-dev  libxvidcore-dev  libx11-dev   libxext-dev   libxfixes-dev  

5) My personal configuration

